<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://focus.nouvelobs.com/2020/03/22/1668/1553/2387/1193/1008/0/50/0/f0f448f_AFP_1Q34SZ.jpg/webp);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1> Pijet brings <strong>data</strong> to <strong>people with a shitty internet connection</strong>!</h1>
    <p>Rent our pigeons and send your data at the speed of light</p>
    <a class="btn btn-flat" href="/pigeons/">Rent a pigeon</a>
    <a class="btn btn-flat" href="/pigeons/new">Earn money with <strong>your </strong>pigeon</a>
  </div>
